snippet.title: Honeycomb - Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Honeycomb is a first-person open-world survival-sandbox where you became a bioengineer.

Steam store page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1510440/Honeycomb/

Greetings explorer! You are going to spend quite some in the laboratory - don’t forget to go on a research expedition into the unknown. A world full of exploration, building and crafting awaits you!

Take on the role of a bioengineer. Conduct research and experiments on flora and fauna. Build, expand, and decorate your habitat, laboratories, and greenhouses in many different ways.

Social media:

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/HoneycombFW
